value.title: Analysis: GOP silence on Trump's false election claims recalls McCarthy era
value.excerpt: The silence of congressional Republican leaders as President Donald Trump's unfounded claims of election fraud grow wilder and more venomous increasingly resembles the party's deference to Sen. Joe McCarthy during the worst excesses of his anti-Communist crusade in the early 1950s.
